{
  "texts": [
    "In oral cancer detection, early diagnosis is vital since it ranks as the sixth most prevalent cancer.",
    "Nayak et al.",
    "(74) demonstrated that AI using laser-induced autofluorescence spectra could accurately distinguish between normal, premalignant, and malignant tissues, suggesting its potential for real-time clinical use.",
    "AI's capabilities in predicting cancer recurrence and assessing lymph node involvement further improve patient care by offering accurate screening tools and personalized treatment approaches.",
    "ChatGPT, in particular, has shown promise in recognizing oral and maxillofacial disorders."
  ]
}